<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>메인 | 갓생 업</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white border-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/main">갓생 업</a>
        <div class="ms-auto d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-secondary small">{{nickname}} 님</span>
            <form method="post" action="/logout" class="m-0">
                <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm">로그아웃</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<main class="container py-4 py-lg-5">
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <section class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-md-center justify-content-between gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-secondary small mb-2">내 캐릭터</p>
                            <h1 class="h3 mb-2">{{nickname}}</h1>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                                <span class="badge text-bg-dark">Lv. {{level}}</span>
                                <span class="badge text-bg-secondary">{{characterName}}</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">
                                EXP {{exp}} / {{requiredExp}}
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="text-center">
                            {{#characterImage}}
                                <img src="{{characterImage}}" alt="{{characterName}}" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-width: 160px;">
                            {{/characterImage}}
                            {{^characterImage}}
                                <div class="border rounded bg-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"
                                     style="width: 160px; height: 160px;">
                                    <span class="text-secondary">{{characterName}}</span>
                                </div>
                            {{/characterImage}}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
                            <span class="small text-secondary">레벨 진행도</span>
                            <span class="small fw-semibold">{{progressPercent}}%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="{{progressPercent}}" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="height: 12px;">
                            <div class="progress-bar" style="width: {{progressPercent}}%;"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-md-center gap-2 mb-4">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-secondary small mb-1">오늘의 퀘스트</p>
                            <h2 class="h4 mb-0">{{today}}</h2>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/missions/new" class="btn btn-dark">미션 등록하기</a>
                    </div>

                    {{^hasTodayMissions}}
                        <div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light text-center text-secondary">
                            오늘 등록된 퀘스트가 없습니다.
                        </div>
                    {{/hasTodayMissions}}

                    {{#hasTodayMissions}}
                        <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
                            {{#todayMissions}}
                                <div class="list-group-item px-0 py-3 bg-transparent">
                                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between gap-3">
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
                                                <span class="badge text-bg-primary">{{difficulty}}</span>
                                                <span class="badge text-bg-light">{{status}}</span>
                                                {{#isModified}}
                                                    <span class="badge text-bg-warning">수정됨</span>
                                                {{/isModified}}
                                            </div>
                                            <h3 class="h6 mb-1">{{content}}</h3>
                                            <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">
                                                날짜: {{missionDate}}
                                            </p>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="text-md-end">
                                            {{#isTodo}}
                                                <a href="/missions/{{id}}/proof" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm mb-2">인증하기</a>
                                                <div>
                                                    <a href="/missions/{{id}}/edit" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">수정하기</a>
                                                </div>
                                            {{/isTodo}}

                                            {{^isTodo}}
                                                <span class="badge text-bg-success mb-2">인증 완료</span>
                                                {{#imageUrl}}
                                                    <div>
                                                        <img src="{{imageUrl}}" alt="인증 사진" class="img-thumbnail" style="width: 88px; height: 88px; object-fit: cover;">
                                                    </div>
                                                {{/imageUrl}}
                                            {{/isTodo}}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            {{/todayMissions}}
                        </div>
                    {{/hasTodayMissions}}
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <section class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-secondary small mb-1">실시간 랭킹</p>
                            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">TOP 5</h2>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/ranking" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm">전체 보기</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        {{#topRankings}}
                            <a href="/user/{{nickname}}" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action px-0 py-3 border-0 border-bottom">
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                                        <img src="{{characterImage}}" alt="{{characterName}}" class="rounded" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; object-fit: contain;">
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="fw-semibold">
                                                {{rank}}위 · {{nickname}}
                                                {{#isMe}}
                                                    <span class="badge text-bg-dark ms-2">Me!</span>
                                                {{/isMe}}
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="small text-secondary">{{characterName}}</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-end">
                                        <div class="small fw-semibold">Lv. {{level}}</div>
                                        <div class="small text-secondary">EXP {{exp}}</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        {{/topRankings}}

                        {{^topRankings}}
                            <div class="text-secondary small">
                                아직 랭킹 데이터가 없습니다.
                            </div>
                        {{/topRankings}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <p class="text-secondary small mb-1">안내</p>
                    <h2 class="h5 mb-3">오늘의 진행 규칙</h2>
                    <ul class="small text-secondary mb-0">
                        <li>난이도별로 하루 1개씩 미션을 등록할 수 있습니다.</li>
                        <li>TODO 상태일 때만 수정이 가능합니다.</li>
                        <li>인증 완료 시 경험치가 즉시 반영됩니다.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
